WEBVTT

00:03:29.750 --> 00:03:32.299
And here's the situation again.

00:03:32.299 --> 00:03:34.851
A is my office,

00:03:34.851 --> 00:03:37.315
B is the place where the duck hit the glass,

00:03:37.315 --> 00:03:40.373
and C is from where I watched it.

00:03:40.373 --> 00:03:43.070
And here are the ducks again.

00:03:43.070 --> 00:03:45.077
As you probably know, in science,

00:03:45.077 --> 00:03:47.260
when you write a kind of special paper,

00:03:47.260 --> 00:03:50.259
only six or seven people read it.

00:03:50.259 --> 00:03:54.984
(Laughter)

00:03:56.844 --> 00:03:59.444
